{"type":"message","id":"23925c01","parentId":"e623a5fb","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:47:17.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to search for images of \"张元英\" (Jang Won-young, a Korean pop idol) on Google. However, I don't have a search tool available in my current toolset. \n\nLooking at my available tools:\n- message: For sending messages and channel actions\n- sessions_list: List sessions\n- sessions_history: Fetch message history\n- sessions_send: Send message to another session\n- session_status: Show session status\n\nI don't have any web search or image search capabilities available. I also received OAuth errors earlier indicating the qwen-portal model authentication has expired.\n\nI should let the user know that I don't have search capabilities available, and suggest they could:\n1. Install a search skill from ClawHub\n2. Do the search themselves directly\n\nLet me be honest about my limitations here.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我目前没有搜索工具可用，无法直接帮你搜索图片。😅\n\n**你可以：**\n\n1. **直接在浏览器搜索：**\n   - 打开 Google 图片\n   - 搜索 \"张元英\" 或 \"Jang Won-young\"\n\n2. **给 OpenClaw 安装搜索技能：**\n   - 访问 https://clawhub.com 查找搜索类技能\n   - 安装后我就能帮你进行搜索了\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你做其他事情吗？📸"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":8200,"output":464,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772855233131}}
