{"type":"message","id":"a263cd8c","parentId":"df688fee","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:48:11.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户询问如何安装 ClawHub 中的技能。我需要提供清晰的安装步骤。根据 OpenClaw 的文档和常见做法，技能安装通常是通过命令行完成的。\n\n让我提供详细的安装指南。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"在 ClawHub 安装技能的步骤：\n\n## 1️⃣ 浏览技能\n\n访问 **https://clawhub.com** 找到你想要的技能包\n\n## 2️⃣ 安装技能\n\n找到技能后，使用以下命令安装：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw skills install <技能包名称>\n```\n\n例如：\n```bash\nopenclaw skills install search\nopenclaw skills install weather\n```\n\n## 3️⃣ 验证安装\n\n安装完成后，检查技能是否成功安装：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw skills list\n```\n\n## 4️⃣ 重启/重载（如需要）\n\n有些技能可能需要重启 OpenClaw 才能生效：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 找不到安装命令？\n\n如果 `openclaw skills install` 命令不可用，可以查看帮助：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw skills --help\n```\n\n或者手动安装：\n1. 从 ClawHub 下载技能包（ZIP 或 Git clone）\n2. 解压到技能目录：\n   ```bash\n   ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/\n   ```\n3. 重启 OpenClaw\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你检查当前已安装的技能吗？📦"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":8387,"output":380,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8767,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772855287323}}
