{"type":"message","id":"6a87775a","parentId":"9f6787d8","timestamp":"2026-03-07T03:50:38.648Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 target 参数不对。根据 inbound context，当前渠道是 webchat，我应该直接用 channel 参数或者不需要指定 target。让我看看之前的成功调用是怎么做的...\n\n看之前的调用，我没有指定 target 或 channel，消息就发送成功了。可能是因为 webchat 渠道会自动路由到当前会话。让我试试只用 message 参数，或者用 channel: webchat。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7448c0ccc1c94261ac7b65d9","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"webchat","message":"对，需要先在 ClawHub 上找到并下载技能包！\n\n## 📥 完整流程：\n\n### 1. 访问 ClawHub\n打开 **https://clawhub.com** 浏览可用的技能\n\n### 2. 下载技能包\n- 找到想要的技能后，点击下载（通常是 ZIP 文件）\n- 或者用 Git clone 如果提供了仓库地址\n\n### 3. 解压到技能目录\n```bash\n# 解压到你下载的位置\nunzip 技能包.zip -d /tmp/skill-temp\n\n# 移动到 OpenClaw 技能目录\nmv /tmp/skill-temp/* ~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/\n```\n\n### 4. 重启 OpenClaw\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 5. 验证安装\n```bash\nopenclaw skills list\n```\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ 或者先看看帮助\n\n运行以下命令查看是否有直接安装的选项：\n```bash\nopenclaw skills --help\n```\n\n如果支持直接从 ClawHub 安装，会有类似 `openclaw skills install <包名>` 的命令。\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你执行这些命令吗？🔧"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen-portal","model":"coder-model","usage":{"input":9656,"output":475,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10131,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772855434370}}
